<section id="commands.groups.math"><title>Math Commands</title>
	
	<para>Standard mathematical functions.</para>

	<section id="command.ref.abs"><title>abs</title>
		<indexterm><primary>commands</primary><secondary>abs</secondary></indexterm>
		<para><emphasis>Syntax:</emphasis></para>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<para> double abs ( int|double num )</para>
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
		<para>Returns the absolute (positively-signed) value of ''num''.</para>
	
	</section>
	
	<section id="command.ref.cos"><title>cos</title>
		<indexterm><primary>commands</primary><secondary>cos</secondary></indexterm>
		<para><emphasis>Syntax:</emphasis></para>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<para> double cos ( double angle )</para>
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
		<para>Returns the cosine of ''angle'' (which should be given in degrees).</para>
	
	</section>
	
